              >
              <div class="flex flex-col ml-6">
                <div class="flex flex-row text-2xl">
                  <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
                    <h1>Product Engineer</h1>
                    <p>
                      At <a class="text-indigo-300" href="https://qbtrix.com/"
                        >Sprinklr</a
                      >
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-2">From July 2022 to Current</p>
                </div>

                <span class="h-0.5 mt-4 w-fill bg-primary bg-opacity-25 rounded-md"></span>

                <ul class="mt-4 text-xl font-light list-disc">
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Working on finance CRM project, where I developed <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">10+ features</span
                    > including <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >collaborative team calendars
                    </span> and <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >voice-notes attachments</span
                    >.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    As part of self-serve product team, worked on <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold"
                      >unified inbox tool</span
                    > that enables users to manage their social media easily & efficiently.
                    Developed <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">25+ complex features, widgets, and improved performance
                    by 30%</span>.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Implemented complex forms with <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">15+ interdependent input
                    fields</span> within work management tool to manage large teams
                    projects & tasks, used by <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">3000+ employees, saving 15% cost</span>
                    of the company, enhancing employee productivity, compliance
                    and data safety.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Contributed to the <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">migration of the entire front-end system</span>
                    to React v18, <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">significantly boosting the performance</span> of our
                    applications.
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2">
                    Delivered a talk on <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">CodeMods</span> and <span
                    class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">Abstract Syntax Tree</span> to
                    <span
                      class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">130+ developers</span>, helping them to automate changes in large
                    scale codebase effectively.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
