                  <p>
                    At <a class="text-indigo-300" href="https://qbtrix.com/"
                      >Sprinklr</a
                    >
                  </p>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-2">From Jan 2022 to June 2022</p>
              </div>

              <span class="h-0.5 mt-4 w-fill bg-primary bg-opacity-25 rounded-md"></span>

              <ul class="mt-4 text-xl font-light list-disc">
                <li class="mb-2">
                  Implemented generalised infra for <span
                  class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">8 apps</span> to enable <span
                  class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">server-side
                  fetching of GraphQL queries</span>.
                </li>
                <li class="mb-2">
                  Introduced eslint rule system to <span
